        <abstract> 
<p>Asks for information on how many languages <hi rend="italic">Origin</hi> has appeared in, how many English and American editions it has gone through, and its reception abroad. Wants to disprove statement that the theory is "fast passing away".</p> 
            <p>Baby ill, scarcely any hope of recovery.</p>
            <p>Some botanical books have come for CD.</p>
        </abstract>
